<plot>PRESS ON is the story of pedal steel phenomenon Robert Randolph and the spiritual tradition in which he was raised. The film follows Robert as he takes this unique "sacred steel" music, which was hidden for over 60 years from the secular world, out of the church and into the mainstream.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?442874</url></doc>
